title: Women in Power: Press for Progress - Politics, Policy, and Pay
description:
In recognition of International Women's Day, Seattle City Councilmembers participate in a discussion about politics, policy, and pay.

Speakers and panelists:
Holly Krejci, Facilities Manager (SDOT)
M. Lorena González, City Councilmember
Lisa Herbold, City Councilmember
Debora Juarez, City Councilmember
Teresa Mosqueda, City Councilmember
Moderator by Maura Brueger, Director of Government and Legislative Affairs (Seattle City Light)
